ITEM: To save your code, you will need to repeatedly click on it until the entire code
is highlighted, then right click it and click copy.
You cannot drag your mouse over the code to copy it as not all will be copied.
Once you have copied the code, you can share it in the forum linked in Notes.
Do not post it in the comments, they will be deleted if you do.
Click Space to confirm that you have read this.
Repeatedly click on the code until it is fully highlighted, then right click it and copy.
